{"tid":176490,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"野豬頭卡鐵欄負傷掙脫","createTime":"2017-03-28T08:17:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T08:34:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"432cd56d457fba6739ff83460c9d9df71d009cf5","tid":176490,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T08:17:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19972190&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170328\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19972190%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170328&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0By7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=f0c08bdb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19972190%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170328&h=84757b12\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19972190&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170328</a><br />\n<br />\n野豬頭卡鐵欄負傷掙脫<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一頭野豬昨晨被困在港島薄扶林一行人路邊鐵欄，頭部夾在鐵枝之間動彈不得。警員接報到場召喚相關部門派員協助，但等候期間野豬自行掙脫，負傷逃往山坡不知所終。<br />\n昨晨10時許，一頭逾一米長的黑色野豬疑四處覓食亂闖，闖到薄扶林域多利道近美景徑時，被行人路與山坡間的一道鐵欄夾着頭部，受傷流血無法脫身。有途人經過發現連忙報警。警員聯同消防員趕到，並通知漁護署派員協助。但在等待期間，野豬自行掙脫，負傷衝落山坡，最後不見蹤影，現場遺下大灘血迹。<br />\n薄扶林不時有野豬出沒，去年12月中，鋼線灣道路邊亦有一頭約200磅重野豬來回踱步，低頭覓食。不少晨運客經過見野豬趣致可愛，紛紛圍觀拍照。最後野豬逗留5分鐘，漫步返回山上。<br />\n■記者文兆麟<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n野豬頭部卡在薄扶林一行人路邊鐵欄。互聯網"},{"pid":"f666b9208efcdad05c8c72e319cf5096b96af18d","tid":176490,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T08:19:26.000Z","msg":"野豬頭部卡在薄扶林一行人路邊鐵欄。互聯網<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170328/large/28la8p04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170328%2Flarge%2F28la8p04.jpg&h=a017e409&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af2c571f5e9c1f0950864abc9008e803da08f2be","tid":176490,"uid":82727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T08:31:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"817d301be75251bc0aa5a47dbb7c8eae4e53aad9","tid":176490,"uid":6098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T08:34:23.000Z","msg":"睇左負傷掙扎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇wu師傅post睇上腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}